commitResults.messageTitle: Add A-BetterGui MainWindow.fxml: Automatically resize elements
commitResults.messageBody:
Some elements do not automatically follow the dimension of app when
resizing:
- TextField does not automatically resize horizontally
- Send button does not follow to the bottom right of the app
- ScrollPane does not automatically resize either horizontally and
vertically

Let's anchor the following nodes:
- Anchor TextField to the bottom while also automatically resizing
horizontally
- Anchor Send Button to the bottom right of the app
- Anchor ScrollPane to resize both horizontally and vertically
